/**
 * Public assets directory structure:
 *
 * public/
 * ├── images/          ← Static images (logo, hero backgrounds, etc.)
 * ├── icons/           ← Favicon, apple-touch-icon, etc.
 * └── og-image.jpg     ← Open Graph preview image (1200×630)
 *
 * Reference in code:   <Image src="/images/logo.svg" ... />
 * These files are served at the root URL path.
 */
